    "long_instructions": "#### Recreate a Song #1\r\n\r\nYour friend, Gemma, heard a great sound combination online. She took a recording of it and is asking you to recreate the sound.\r\n\r\nDo this: \r\n\r\n- Listen to the song in the music player called \"Gemma's Song\". \r\n- Use the sounds given to you to build the song. \r\n- Look at the timeline image below as reference.\r\n\r\n![](https://images.code.org/3899b4f06e1afcab08fa6080c0359192-image-1741387084637.37.44 PM.png)",
